Places like: Target, AppleBee's, BBQs, Chipotle, Chase, Children's Place, Men's Warehouse, David's Bridal, T-Mobile, 7/11, BP Gas Station, McDonalds, Payless, Little Cesar's, MET Supermarkets, Clean Rite 24/7 Laundry Service, TD Bank, YMCA, Starbucks, Burger King, Dollar Tree, Modell's, GNC...are literally steps away!!!

Make yourself as comfortable as possible. I provide literally everything that you'll need! ENJOY
additional_house_rules: - Please NO smoking inside the apartment, the outside stairwell or the hallway. If you must smoke, please smoke outside of the building.   You may play music loudly on Friday afternoon-Sunday afternoon. No crazy insane parties or drug use inside the apartment! No loud music playing Sunday night-Friday morning. However, on the weekend have a BLAST! You're in New York and your neighbors are insanely cool, no one will bother you!   No running, jumping or stomping in apartment. Remember, this is New York City apartment living and you have neighbors who live beneath you. Music playing is fine!  Do NOT remove any of the amenities provided! You have free use of them but PLEASE do not take them with you after your stay. DO NOT leave soiled dishes in the sink. DO NOT rearrange any of the furniture. Lastly, have FUN and WELCOME TO NEW YORK!
description:
Extra large fully equipped studio w/4 big beds in lovely Ditmas Park, BK. Just a 10min commute to beautiful Prospect Park & Kings Plaza Mall! & LIRR train 25mins to magnificent Times Sq-42nd street! Super accessible public transportation options just steps away!
Enjoy the DAILY BREAKFAST,  the diverse neighborhood, the freedom to play music on the weekends & safe & secluded enough for relaxation and privacy. Visit NY for less and enjoy what the Big Apple has to offer!

This is an XTRA large studio, that's furnished like a 1-2 bedroom apartment! can be converted to a 1 bedroom by simply drawing close the curtained room divider (it's very thick and NOT see through). Pay the price of a studio with the amenities of a 1-2 bedroom!  


Perfect for the person who doesn't like clutter! My place has a very minimalistic feel without sacrificing amenities that will make your stay ultra comfortable and carefree. 

There are 4 BEDS: 1 Queen sized (double) mattress, 1 Queen sized air mattress (not pictured) and 2 twin size mattresses

The entire apartment. 

There is also a printer/copier/scanner, PS4 with 2 controllers, 4 BEDS, two 10lbs dumbbells, coffee maker with unlimited coffee, pull up bar, work out mat, and even a tripod you can use for your professional camera while traveling around the city! 

BREAKFAST DAILY: Unlimited coffee/tea/filtered water & oatmeal,eggs,cheese,breakfast bars, fruit & hot chocolate & other breakfast foods

There are many vegan/vegetarian/Mexican/Carribbean/American restaurants and bars within a short distance away! 

Places like: Target, AppleBee's, BBQs, Chipotle, Chase, Children's Place, Men's Warehouse, David's Bridal, T-Mobile, 7/11, BP Gas Station, McDonalds, Payless, Little Cesar's, MET Supermarkets, Clean Rite 24/7 Laundry Service, TD Bank, YMCA, Starbucks, Burger King, Dollar Tree, Modell's, GNC...are literally steps away!!!

Make yourself as comfortable as possible. I provide literally everything that you'll need! ENJOY

I will always be just a phone call or text message away! However, you'll be staying in the unit by yourself or with your travel buddies. I don't drop by unless you need me!

The diversity and the chill vibe! No pretentiousness, boring feel or super strict neighborhood rules. Super safe (police pct is walking distance) and a well established neighborhood of professionals! Perfect for families with small and older children, business professionals who need easy access to the city but enough quietness to get work done and large groups of younger people who want to be close to NY's nightlife and be able to play music on the weekends without being bothered!

Many buses, trains and "$2 dollar vans" that can get you to downtown Brooklyn (think: Brooklyn Bridge) within 20 mins, the city (think Times Sq) within 25mins and Prospect Park is a 15 walk/jog min away or 10 min "$2 dollar van" ride away! The LIRR (Long Island Rail Road) is a quick commute away and can get you to midtown/34-42nd street area in 20 mins!

DAILY BREAKFAST!!!

FREE WIFI!!

FREE UNLIMITED COFFEE/TEA!! 

FREE USE OF PS4, NETFLIX and Fire Stick!!!

Feel free to use anything you need in the home! Check the photos for descriptions of more of what's provided!

hosts.about:
Hey!

I am a native New Yorker and a huge fan of Airbnb. I've been staying in others homes for years and was inspired to share my awesome apartment to others as well! 

I love all things New York and I've lived here my entire life (nearly every borough!). Feel free to ask me any questions! I'm here to help make your stay comfortable, enjoyable and of course FUN!

photos.caption: EXTRA LARGE studio that sleeps 8 comfortably. 4 available beds and loads of closet and sitting space. Perfect for you to enjoy your NY stay!
DREAM peacefully on this super comfortable pillow top covered Queen mattress. 1 of 4 available beds!

Long sectional w/throw pillows, area rug and coffee table. Perfect for a cozy night in to watch a movie on the 32inch LCD flatscreen or play a few games on the PS4. Or perfect for relaxing with your friends and pregaming until it's time to go out for the night. Or perfect to let the kids curl up and watch cartoons on Fire Stick.
Turn the studio into a 1 bedroom by keeping the curtained (not see through) room divider closed. On the other side is a large area furnished with a full size bed!
Sit at this vintage oak wood table with your family, spouse or friends, light a candle, play soft music from the flatscreen tv and enjoy the warmth of togetherness during your stay.

Lots of hangers of different styles available to you to stay and live as comfortable as possible and not out of your suitcase! Extra large closet space! (Queen sized electronic air mattress, iron, extra bicycle seat cushion, 10lb dumbbells, tripod and shopping cart inside)
Extra large and wide mirror. This mirror is about 6ft5inches high! Be confident in knowing that you look amazing and see your outfit from all different angles!

Desk/Workspace with Makeup/Beauty Desk...equipped with pens/highlighters, USB cords, stapler w/stables, tissues. A pull out keyboard shelf. As well as a WIFI enabled printer/copier/scanner with extra computer paper and a laptop resting mount if you rather sit on the couch than at the desk/workspace. As well as a perfect mirror for makeup application and organizers for makeup kits and palettes. Arranged to bring in natural light while you're working/applying makeup. (Black ottoman for sitting here)

Kitchen fully stocked with utensils, pots/pans, bowls, pots/pans, seasonings for all types of cooking, Microwave, Crockpot and coffee maker (stocked with everything to make yourself FREE UNLIMITED coffee during your stay!)

Full bathroom with all amenities: TOP: blow dryer, flat iron, hand held mirror, MIDDLE: towels, wash cloths BOTTOM: toilet tissue, flushable wipes, cotton swabs, cotton balls, brush, comp, extra toothbrushes, body freshener spray, tampons, panty liners, bandaids, nasal strips, toothpicks, lint brush, body lotion, air freshener SINK: toothpaste,hand soap, toothbrush holder SHOWER: conditioner, shampoo, body scrub, body wash FLOOR: scale CABINET: over the counter medicine
Full bathroom with all amenities including a scale!

2 pillow top twin size mattresses. Extra comfortable! Separated by curtained (not see through) room divider! With bookshelf filled with board and card games (Cards of Humanity, Monopoly, Jenga ,Checkers, Uno, Connect Four etc!)
